						<summary>

						<p>This records the gift of a <hi rend="italic">dīpamāle</hi> (lights) to a god (name not clear) by Bukkayave the <hi rend="italic">ardhāṅgalakshmi</hi> (queen) of Vīra Harihararāya (Harihara II) for the merit of her spiritual teacher Bhāskaradēvayya. The date is given as Īśvara (Śaka 1319), Mārgaśira śu. [9], Tuesday = A.D. 1397, November 29, Thursday (not Tuesday). </p>						

